<item>
            <title>[HBASE-903] [shell] Can&apos;t set table descriptor attributes when I alter a table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-903</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I wanted to set the compaction filesize attribute but no good:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;hbase(main):005:0&amp;gt; alter &apos;TestTable&apos;, {MAX_FILESIZE =&amp;gt; 67108864} 
TypeError: can&apos;t convert Hash into &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;
	from /Users/stack/Documents/checkouts/hbase/trunk/bin/../bin/HBase.rb:138:in `hcd&apos;
	from /Users/stack/Documents/checkouts/hbase/trunk/bin/../bin/HBase.rb:138:in `alter&apos;
	from /Users/stack/Documents/checkouts/hbase/trunk/bin/../bin/hirb.rb:239:in `alter&apos;
	from (hbase):6:in `binding&apos;
hbase(main):006:0&amp;gt; alter &apos;TestTable&apos;, {MAX_FILESIZE =&amp;gt; 67108864}

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
